        {
            "id": 3,
            "module": "ai-local-agent:RunLocalAIAgent",
            "version": 0,
            "parameters": {
                "makeConnectionId": null
            },
            "mapper": {
                "files": [],
                "message": "{{2.answers.`YOUR_QUESTION_ID`.textAnswers.answers[].value}}",
                "timeout": "",
                "threadId": "",
                "outputType": "make-schema",
                "modelConfig": {
                    "recursionLimit": 300,
                    "iterationsFromHistoryCount": "10"
                },
                "defaultModel": "gpt-4o",
                "outputSchema": [
                    {
                        "help": "Whether the feedback is positive or negative",
                        "name": "sentiment",
                        "type": "text",
                        "label": "Sentiment",
                        "default": "",
                        "required": true,
                        "multiline": false
                    }
                ],
                "systemPrompt": "You are a **Customer Feedback Sentiment Analyzer**. Your job is to read customer feedback text and output a **single sentiment label**: **positive** or **negative**.\n\n## What you analyze\n- Focus primarily on the customer's **overall emotion and satisfaction**.\n- Use the whole message, but weight **conclusions** and **strong statements** more than minor side-notes.\n\n## Output rules (strict)\n- Output **only one word**: `positive` or `negative`\n- Use **lowercase only**\n- No punctuation, no explanations, no extra fields, no JSON.\n\n## Classification guidance\nClassify as **positive** when the feedback is predominantly:\n- satisfied, happy, grateful, praising, recommending, impressed, problem resolved, good experience\n\nClassify as **negative** when the feedback is predominantly:\n- dissatisfied, frustrated, complaining, warning others, requesting refund/cancel, unresolved issue, bad experience\n\n## Edge cases\n- **Mixed feedback**: choose the **dominant** sentiment; if the customer ends with dissatisfaction or an unresolved problem, label **negative**.\n- **Neutral/unclear/too short** (e.g., \"ok\", \"fine\", \"N/A\", empty): label **negative** (default to conservative).\n- **Sarcasm**: classify based on the implied meaning (e.g., \"Great, it broke again\" → negative).\n- **Support requests**: if it's mainly a complaint/request for help, label **negative** unless clearly appreciative and satisfied.\n\n## Ignore\n- Personal data, order numbers, signatures, greetings—these should not affect sentiment.",
                "reasoningEffort": "medium"
            },
            "metadata": {
                "designer": {
                    "x": 300,
                    "y": 300,
                    "name": "Customer Feedback Agent"
                },
                "restore": {
                    "expect": {
                        "files": {
                            "mode": "chose"
                        },
                        "outputType": {
                            "label": "Data structure"
                        },
                        "defaultModel": {
                            "mode": "chose",
                            "label": "GPT-4o"
                        },
                        "outputSchema": {
                            "items": [
                                null
                            ]
                        },
                        "reasoningEffort": {
                            "mode": "chose",
                            "label": "Medium"
                        }
                    },
                    "parameters": {
                        "makeConnectionId": {
                            "data": {
                                "scoped": "true",
                                "connection": "ai-provider"
                            },
                            "label": "Your AI Provider Connection"
                        }
                    }
                },
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "makeConnectionId",
                        "type": "account:ai-provider,openai-gpt-3,anthropic-claude,gemini-ai-q9zyjp,ai-agent-foundry-openai,ai-agent-foundry-non-openai,mistral-ai,cohere,groq,ai-agent-xai,amazon-bedrock,ai-agent-openai-compatible",
                        "label": "Connection",
                        "required": true
                    }
                ],
                "expect": [
                    {
                        "name": "defaultModel",
                        "type": "select",
                        "label": "Model",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "reasoningEffort",
                        "type": "select",
                        "label": "Reasoning effort",
                        "validate": {
                            "enum": ["none", "low", "medium", "high"]
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "systemPrompt",
                        "type": "text",
                        "label": "Instructions"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "message",
                        "type": "text",
                        "label": "Input",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "files",
                        "spec": [
                            {
                                "name": "fileName",
                                "type": "filename",
                                "label": "File name",
                                "semantic": "file:name"
                            },
                            {
                                "name": "data",
                                "type": "buffer",
                                "label": "Data",
                                "semantic": "file:data"
                            }
                        ],
                        "type": "array",
                        "label": "Input files"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "threadId",
                        "type": "text",
                        "label": "Conversation ID"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "modelConfig",
                        "spec": [
                            {
                                "name": "tokenLimit",
                                "type": "hidden",
                                "label": "Max output tokens"
                            },
                            {
                                "name": "recursionLimit",
                                "type": "hidden",
                                "label": "Steps per agent call"
                            },
                            {
                                "name": "iterationsFromHistoryCount",
                                "type": "number",
                                "label": "Maximum conversation history"
                            }
                        ],
                        "type": "collection",
                        "label": "Model configuration"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "timeout",
                        "type": "number",
